, \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 23439, \"end\": 23455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"score\": 0.9999993389976591, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kristen Faulkner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\ud83c\\uddf8\", \"from\": 23293, \"to\": 23294}, {\"ngram\": \"OlympicCycling\", \"from\": 23364, \"to\": 23378}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris2024\", \"from\": 23380, \"to\": 23389}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish\", \"from\": 23460, \"to\": 23470}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 23490, \"to\": 23497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I took a really big risk a few years ago to come to pursue my dream and I made it happen.\", \"from\": 23511, \"to\": 23600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really big risk\", \"from\": 23518, \"to\": 23535}, {\"ngram\": \"my dream\", \"from\": 23570, \"to\": 23578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the best feeling in the world, I do not know how to describe it.\\\"\", \"from\": 23601, \"to\": 23671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best feeling\", \"from\": 23606, \"to\": 23622}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 23626, \"to\": 23635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you hope to win solo?\", \"from\": 23673, \"to\": 23698, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"solo\", \"from\": 23693, \"to\": 23697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had high hopes.\", \"from\": 23700, \"to\": 23718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high hopes\", \"from\": 23707, \"to\": 23717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am racing team pursuit in two days and so I said I'd only do the road race if I felt strong and felt I had a chance of a medal.\", \"from\": 23719, \"to\": 23848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"team pursuit\", \"from\": 23731, \"to\": 23743}, {\"ngram\": \"two days\", \"from\": 23747, \"to\": 23755}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 23782, \"to\": 23795}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 23828, \"to\": 23836}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 23840, \"to\": 23847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew that it would be a really tough race but if I was racing, I was racing to win.\", \"from\": 23849, \"to\": 23934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really tough race\", \"from\": 23873, \"to\": 23892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a promise I made to my team pursuit teammates.\\\"\", \"from\": 23935, \"to\": 23991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a promise\", \"from\": 23944, \"to\": 23953}, {\"ngram\": \"my team\", \"from\": 23964, \"to\": 23971}, {\"ngram\": \"pursuit teammates\", \"from\": 23972, \"to\": 23989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What was the plan with the final?\", \"from\": 23993, \"to\": 24026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the plan\", \"from\": 24002, \"to\": 24010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew that Kopeckly wanted to catch the front two, so I knew she'd ride with me.\", \"from\": 24028, \"to\": 24110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kopeckly\", \"from\": 24041, \"to\": 24049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also knew that if we caught them, then I had to attack because I could not beat any of them at the line.\", \"from\": 24111, \"to\": 24217, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 24208, \"to\": 24216}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew the best place to attack was right after we caught them and everyone was tied.\", \"from\": 24218, \"to\": 24303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best place\", \"from\": 24225, \"to\": 24239}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 24285, \"to\": 24293}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was my chance.\", \"from\": 24304, \"to\": 24323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my chance\", \"from\": 24313, \"to\": 24322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I practised my late attack several times this year, so I felt pretty comfortable with how to do it.\", \"from\": 24324, \"to\": 24423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my late attack\", \"from\": 24336, \"to\": 24350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just hoped it worked.\\\"\", \"from\": 24424, \"to\": 24448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you know you'd won?\", \"from\": 24450, \"to\": 24473, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was pretty sure I'd won but it was like 'what in the world just happened?'\", \"from\": 24475, \"to\": 24552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 24527, \"to\": 24536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not process it.\", \"from\": 24553, \"to\": 24576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It took me a few minutes.\", \"from\": 24577, \"to\": 24602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had to double and triple check that I won gold.\", \"from\": 24603, \"to\": 24652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 24647, \"to\": 24651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew it but I did not know it.\\\"\", \"from\": 24653, \"to\": 24686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Make sure you have a read of our post race report by clicking the link below... >>>Paris Olympics: Kristen Faulkner shocks favourites with solo victory in women's road race In Bronze, Lotte Kopecky (Belgium).\", \"from\": 24690, \"to\": 24902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24781, \"end\": 24795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 24797, \"end\": 24813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kristen_Faulkner\", \"score\": 0.9999993389976591, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\":